<p>So here's my first contribution to the 'War on all Fronts' canon. <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">I'll be posting another one tomorrow, and most of you will have no trouble guessing which GoI that will be.</span></p>
<p><strong>Edit:</strong> Change of plans. Due to the lukewarm reception the base article has received it's being rewritten, and at storm's request I am holding off on posting my second contribution until it's up.</p>
<p>Thanks especially to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516659722" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span> for conceiving and spearheading this project, as well as to all my other beta readers: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bear-run" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1766089); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1766089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516659722" alt="Bear-run" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1766089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bear-run" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1766089); return false;">Bear-run</a></span> Dr J No <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(17670); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=17670&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516659722" alt="Macleod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=17670)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(17670); return false;">Macleod</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3489662); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3489662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1516659722" alt="mayoculpa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/u