			<div class="content" id="post-content-3689456">
									

<p>That's fair as well. My response to that would be that Ruprecht's avoided capture for so long because he's rich, not because he's smart (Trump, basically). The financial and anomalous resources at MC&amp;D's disposal make them a force to be reckoned with, and are more than sufficient to get their board members out of any jams they may end up in.</p>
<p>Whenever MC&amp;D pops up in Dread &amp; Circuses (which this technically isn't but I'm still counting it in that continuity) Percival/Iris are the brains of the operation, Amos Marshall is the shrewd businessman, and Carter is a Rich Idiot With No Day Job.</p>

