<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-385543-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-385543-2')">2</a>. From Proto-Uralic <em>*ńä(x)li</em> + <em>*-ka</em>, meaning &quot;hunger&quot;.</div>
