			<div class="content" id="post-content-3698032">
									

<p>I upvoted it at first. But after not very long consideration I changed my vote to -1.<br />
And that's why:<br />
Accept for the part of Carter idea go wrong, it's very similar to <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/imperfectly-fossilized-eggs-m4rho-edope-fo5le">one more MC&amp;D delicacy</a>, which is also a rear egg on the plate. Literally. And it does not have any outstanding features of it's own. So it's basically a not very good copy. But the part with Carter is catchy. Maybe you should reimagine the merchandise part for something completely different, and extend the Carter fail part, or put more string to it.</p>
<p>P.S. For some reason it's not the first duplication work which came recently.<br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3813">Ancient war elephant</a> made by a team of very famous authors has the same problem. And strangely to me has a very high rate. I just hope this is not new thread of community.</p>

