<p>[<em><span style="color: blue"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">citation needed</span></span></em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]</span></p>
<p>In all seriousness though, I'm not sure I'm understanding where you're coming from. If anything, we're deleting a <em>lot</em> more things these days than we were a few years ago (of course, the increase in volume of coldposted works also contributes to that).</p>
